We chanced upon a lone house, heavily fortified and surrounded by barriacades and entrenchments, the struture had the look of a makeshift fortress but of the occupants we saw no sign. Despite an apparent absence of tenets, the house looked to have been as yet unpillaged and presented a tempting target. Andy suggested proceeding with caution and so I: 

 [BUTTON](Scenario_PreAlpha_FortifiedHouse_A){Heeded his advice and advanced cautionly into the building} 

 [BUTTON](Scenario_PreAlpha_FortifiedHouse_B){Ignored his blubbering and strode confidently into the building} [EXIT_BUTTON]
